data.description: This like new End Unit customized Covington Model with full brick front and side water-table will take be the ONE!  Includes an oversized rear 2 car garage, redesigned lower level with wood flooring, barn sliding doors, separate office, and spacious fourth bedroom with full bath, a gourmet kitchen with stunning white Shaker-style cabinetry, 15’ center island with brilliant white quartz counters and upgraded stainless steel appliances with French bottom freezer refrigerator, wall ovens, gas cooktop, and vented chimney hood. This home offers an open design that is perfect for entertaining or larger gathers. With impressive features such as a 10' extension, multiple entertaining areas, gleaming wide plank hardwood covers the entire 1st floor, 2nd floor & 3rd floor hall and stairs to all levels. The kitchen level includes a large family area that connects to an oversized composite deck. On the bedroom level there are three bedrooms with 2 full baths, and laundry room with cabinets, laundry tub, and washer/dryer. The owner’s suite has 2 walk-in closets, tray ceiling with 10’ center, private bath, with free standing garden tub, 8’ shower with frameless door and mud-set pan. Nestled among the lush tree preserve and winding creeks, Woodlands at Goose Creek offers homeowners a luxurious and peaceful retreat within the surroundings of historic Leesburg, VA. Within walking distance to Village of Leesburg, shopping and dining plus the everyday conveniences you will find everything you need and more.
